{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00150/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00150"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:01:50"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man pulls his pants on and tucks his shirt in, looking in a mirror offscreen."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00150","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00150"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1/c2747613-2cb5-4c4d-82d1-5c78c749406d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:09:00.922Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>After a series of close-ups and medium shots, the camera backs away and presents Reynolds at full height—putting on his trousers. For a film driven by pent-up urges, this is perhaps its most risqué moment. It marks an inversion of where the film ends—with Reynolds needing to pull down his pants in a bathroom prepped for the mushroom-induced mess that will come spilling out of him.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:937.1605839416058,454.31386861313865,273.05474452554756,588.7773722627738"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1/43ca76d6-6c56-4578-8f00-a9c6d1202984","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:09:29.237Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Audiences see Reynolds through an open door, looking in from what seems to be the bathroom. This only reinforces the intimate and clandestine tenor of our voyeurism as spectators.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00150/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1225.4